{"tid":640267,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連加特：我無選擇去利物浦，因為有次比賽無人傳波比我！","createTime":"2018-04-24T07:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T17:42:19.000Z","uid":8968,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"78f80fdc497ab678afc6c912a06d87b202ca6fa6","tid":640267,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:13:36.000Z","msg":"曼聯中場連加特近日接受了英國每日郵報的採訪，他在訪問時向記者透露，他在小時候曾經有機會加盟利物浦踢青年軍，不過在當地的某一場場比賽有隊友沒有選擇傳波給他，因為這樣受到忽視，令他隨後選擇去到了現在的球隊，曼聯。<br />\n　　<br />\n就在連加特只有7歲的時候，他曾經去過代表利物浦和曼聯的青年軍比賽，而那些比賽的性質類似試腳的形式。而每逢有這些比賽，連加特的爺爺都會送他去比賽，他的爺爺在日常生活都主要負責照顧連加特。<br />\n　<br />\n連加特講述當日比賽發生的事：那天我在利物浦比賽，不過有人在我已經取得空位的情況下沒有傳球予我，而這件事亦發生過不只一次，我當下的想法是：我不能再這樣了，我從球場走向爺爺並對他說我希望去曼聯。這就是我現在在這裡（曼聯）的原因。<br />\n<br />\n連加特向他的爺爺說自己在曼聯的感覺很舒服，而且自己十分喜歡這裡。而他的爺爺也有支持他的決定，直到現在，他的爺爺都會入場看連加特的比賽，在比賽前亦會向連加特發短信讓他加油。<br />\n<br />\n連加特指曼聯的工作人員當時做過了很多不同種類的測試，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">判定出他的發育階段是比較遲緩的</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以費格遜當時亦有向我的家人解釋，讓他們知道要相信球會，他們的兒子正在向正確的方向成長。費格遜向我的家人強調我終有一天可以代表曼聯上陣，這亦讓我的爸爸和爺爺感到放心，讓我留在曼聯。我亦十分相信費格遜，我十分尊敬他和感激他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/manmancome/%EF%BC%BB%E5%94%94%E8%AC%9B%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5%EF%BC%BD%E9%80%A3%E5%8A%A0%E7%89%B9-%E6%88%91%E7%84%A1%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87%E5%8E%BB%E5%88%A9%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%A6-%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%89%E6%AC%A1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B3%E6%B3%A2%E6%AF%94%E6%88%91-c1318213.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fmanmancome%2F%25EF%25BC%25BB%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%259F%25A5%25EF%25BC%25BD%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%2589%25B9-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2593%2587%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25B5%25A6-%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%25AF%2594%25E6%2588%2591-c1318213.html&d=dwnxjq7AAAmXthCMTWeEysmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=eadd0365\" target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/manmancome/%EF%BC%BB%E5%94%94%E8%AC%9B%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5%EF%BC%BD%E9%80%A3%E5%8A%A0%E7%89%B9-%E6%88%91%E7%84%A1%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87%E5%8E%BB%E5%88%A9%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%A6-%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%89%E6%AC%A1%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B3%E6%B3%A2%E6%AF%94%E6%88%91-c1318213.html</a>"},{"pid":"0be4aba5fa8d14d5413bbd9fa607874902f6ff58","tid":640267,"uid":8968,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/9oIrtP38K5Ofl5qLzT/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9oIrtP38K5Ofl5qLzT%2Fgiphy.gif&h=abf2a39c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6a10e6b5841a8213f41e51e274153f5bbbea95c","tid":640267,"uid":136116,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"估唔到利記青年隊啲人咁年紀咁細智商已經咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d44c8653a4a1faa5d34b8f56ff6dec109f636a6","tid":640267,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0c75cb247feac1eed4652807c29cd0dc839949","tid":640267,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d44c8653a4a1faa5d34b8f56ff6dec109f636a6","tid":640267,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T